# Development Workflow

# ========================================

# Daily Development

```bash
npm run start:dev       # Start API with watch mode
npm run start:debug     # Start API with debugger + watch mode
```

# Database Operations

```bash
npm run db:up           # Start Postgres + pgAdmin via Docker, then run migrations
npm run migrate         # Run database migrations only
npm run seed            # Seed database with initial data
```

# Code Quality

```bash
npm run lint            # ESLint with auto-fix
npm run format          # Prettier formatting
npm run type-check      # TypeScript type validation (tsc --noEmit)
```

# Testing

```bash
npm run test            # Run all tests (Jest)
npm run test:watch      # Run tests in watch mode
npm run test:cov        # Run tests with coverage
npm run test:e2e        # Run e2e tests
```

# ========================================

# Common Patterns

# ========================================

# Module Creation

```typescript
@Module({
  controllers: [FeatureController],
  providers: [FeatureService, FeatureRepository],
  exports: [FeatureService],
})
export class FeatureModule {}
```

Note: `DatabaseModule` is `@Global()` — no need to import it in feature modules.

# Controller Pattern

```typescript
@Controller('features')
@ApiTags('Features')
@ApiBearerAuth()
export class FeatureController {
  constructor(private readonly featureService: FeatureService) {}

  @Get()
  @ApiOperation({ summary: 'List features for current tenant' })
  @ApiResponse({ status: 200, type: [FeatureResponseDto] })
  async findAll(@CurrentUser() user: AuthenticatedUser) {
    return this.featureService.findAll(user.tenantId);
  }
}
```

# Service Pattern

```typescript
@Injectable()
export class FeatureService {
  constructor(private readonly featureRepository: FeatureRepository) {}

  async findAll(tenantId: string): Promise<Feature[]> {
    return this.featureRepository.findAllByTenant(tenantId);
  }
}
```

# DTO Pattern

```typescript
export class CreateFeatureDto {
  @ApiProperty({ description: 'Feature name' })
  @IsString()
  @IsNotEmpty()
  name: string;

  @ApiProperty({ description: 'Feature description', required: false })
  @IsString()
  @IsOptional()
  description?: string;
}
```

